[UI/SidepanelOutfitsView]
- dependency : UI-Base
- added   : abstract LLPanelOutfitsTab class to break LLPanelOutfitsInventory's direct dependency on LLOutfitsList
- added   : specialized inventory view of the "My Outfits" in the Appearance sidebar panel (see LLOutfitsView class)
- added   : "UseOutfitInventoryView" setting to switch between the default accordion view and the new inventory view (defaults to inventory view)
- changed : show the target attachment point for worn attachments in a wearable item list (see "Wearing" outfit panel)
- changed : worn item colour in a wearable item list from green (=EmphasisColor) to white (=default colour)
